{"tid":649390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"22歲女警涉偷1.3萬元護膚品","createTime":"2018-05-01T14:00:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-01T14:21:49.000Z","uid":81228,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6302e1638f138af31a3a70b313fc0470a5351d","tid":649390,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T14:00:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180426/large/26ls3p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180426%2Flarge%2F26ls3p1.jpg&h=aaa94f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告女警李慧玲被控4項盜竊罪，昨日提堂。陳善南攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】年輕女警涉於今年2月至3月休班期間，4次到萬寧的3間分店偷竊共29件護膚產品，總值逾1.3萬元。女警被控4項盜竊罪，昨在九龍城法院提堂。辯方申請押後答辯，以便索取控方文件及精神科醫生報告，同事透露被告一直有向精神科求診，法庭批准申請，被告獲准保釋至6月20日再訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>四度於萬寧犯案</strong><br />\n<br />\n被告李慧玲（22歲）昨由數名親友陪同到庭應訊，坐在旁聽席等候傳召期間，被告一直表現緊張，應訊後戴上鴨舌帽，以手遮擋面容離開。4項盜竊罪指她於本年2月15日至3月9日間，先後於青衣青衣城1期、旺角新世紀廣場及觀塘德福廣場的萬寧分店，分別盜取8件、11件、7件和3件護膚產品，總值逾1.3萬元。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：KCCC1248/18<br />\n■記者羅日昇、蔡少玲<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373149\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373149&d=ezadUHsncOyg%2Flh2GMxjIi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=0f33d1b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180426%2F20373149&h=d89b85c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180426/20373149</a>"},{"pid":"03ab22874c2bbbc3f5734898828ba645b97d16f2","tid":649390,"uid":110134,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T14:01:43.000Z","msg":"休班警+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae72ba656476f43bf045e8f2eb1f12befd746b0","tid":649390,"uid":36964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-01T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"收2皮人工 知法犯法<im